(168, '_transient_ti_about_plugin_info_otter-blocks', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":20:{s:4:\"name\";s:46:\"Gutenberg Blocks and Template Library by Otter\";s:4:\"slug\";s:12:\"otter-blocks\";s:7:\"version\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:6:\"author\";s:45:\"<a href=\"https://themeisle.com\">ThemeIsle</a>\";s:14:\"author_profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/themeisle\";s:12:\"contributors\";a:2:{s:9:\"themeisle\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:40:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/themeisle\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a0ec097eaf5f30933eb00c1175d4bd55?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:9:\"Themeisle\";}s:13:\"hardeepasrani\";a:3:{s:7:\"profile\";s:44:\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hardeepasrani\";s:6:\"avatar\";s:88:\"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/33cc57ef37124a38cf019747c0880172?s=96&d=monsterid&r=g\";s:12:\"display_name\";s:14:\"Hardeep Asrani\";}}s:12:\"requires_php\";s:3:\"5.4\";s:7:\"ratings\";a:5:{i:5;i:15;i:4;i:0;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:1;}s:11:\"num_ratings\";i:16;s:15:\"support_threads\";i:10;s:24:\"support_threads_resolved\";i:8;s:15:\"active_installs\";i:10000;s:8:\"homepage\";s:42:\"https://themeisle.com/plugins/otter-blocks\";s:8:\"sections\";a:4:{s:11:\"description\";s:1591:\"<p>Gutenberg Blocks and Template Library by Otter is a lightweight WordPress plugin that brings extra Gutenberg blocks to your site. So if you want to create complex pages and posts optimized for e-commerce, business, social media, blogs &#8211; you name it -comes with dozens of Gutenberg blocks that are all you need to build beautiful pages.</p>\n<p>See what you can do with Otter:</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe class=\'youtube-player\' type=\'text/html\' width=\'640\' height=\'360\' src=\'https://www.youtube.com/embed/ypIeTgvYeRE?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;autohide=2&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent\' allowfullscreen=\'true\' style=\'border:0;\'></iframe></span></p>\n<p>A feature that is worth mentioning is the Section Block that allows you to build columns and various layouts in Gutenberg. Moreover, aside from the Gutenberg blocks, the plugin provides a beautiful library of pre-built Gutenberg-compatible templates that you can simply import via one click. The templates have block-friendly layouts that can be customized with no effort.</p>\n<p>Every block can be customized in a few seconds, as they come with an easy and intuitive user</p>\n<p>It has:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Section Block</li>\n<li>Advanced Heading Block</li>\n<li>Button Group</li>\n<li>Service Block</li>\n<li>Pricing Block</li>\n<li>Testimonial Block</li>\n<li>Google Maps Block</li>\n<li>About Author Block</li>\n<li>Post Grid Block</li>\n<li>Font Awesome Block</li>\n<li>Sharing Icons Block</li>\n<li>Plugin Card Block</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:3848:\"<h4>1.2.3 &#8211; 2019-05-24</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add BlockInserter</li>\n<li>Google Maps Improvements</li>\n<li>Link Component Improvements</li>\n<li>Fix Sizing Control value type</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2 &#8211; 2019-05-08</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add HTML Anchor to Section Block.</li>\n<li>Change Default Section setting.</li>\n<li>Fix resizer styles.</li>\n<li>Add Link Component.</li>\n<li>Add Marker button to Map.</li>\n<li>Remove Padding Resizer.</li>\n<li>Better UI for Sizing Control.</li>\n<li>Fix Dynamic CSS not rendering on reusable blocks.</li>\n<li>Validate blocks before importing.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1 &#8211; 2019-04-20</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed issue with constant not being checked in Otter</li>\n<li>Added error handling in Backbone functions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.0 &#8211; 2019-04-18</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Otter Option page</li>\n<li>Added update notice on Template Library</li>\n<li>Redesigned Google Map block</li>\n<li>Redesigned Post Grid block</li>\n<li>Removed Handsontable from Chart block</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5 &#8211; 2019-03-08</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Redesign Template Library</li>\n<li>Added Dynamic Column Resizing</li>\n<li>Added option to Auto Display Columns on Pages</li>\n<li>Added Section Outline to make it easier to edit sections</li>\n<li>Added Hover and Link settings to Font Awesome Block</li>\n<li>Removed Google + icon from Sharing Icons Block</li>\n<li>Fixed alignment controls</li>\n<li>Fixed issue with non-editors not being able to use inline CSS and template library.</li>\n<li>Fixed Button Group errors</li>\n<li>Fixed Sharing Icons block having wrong icon order in front-end</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4 &#8211; 2019-01-31</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Font Awesome Block update path</li>\n<li>Show selected font in Google Font picker</li>\n<li>Fix Font Awesome Picker component being case-sensitive</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3 &#8211; 2019-01-30</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds Feedback for Button Group Switch</li>\n<li>Fixes Post Grid throwing an error</li>\n<li>Fixes issue with multiple block templates being inserted on the same post</li>\n<li>Fixes Font Awesome block alignment on the backend</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2 &#8211; 2019-01-28</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Button Group Migration</li>\n<li>Revamped Font Awesome Icon Picker</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1 &#8211; 2019-01-25</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Developer Documentation</li>\n<li>Added Typography Option to Block Toolbar</li>\n<li>Fixed Padding Resizer</li>\n<li>Made Template Library Responsive</li>\n<li>Fixed Close Icon Alignment on Chrome</li>\n<li>Fixed Alignment with Span Tag in Advanced Heading Block</li>\n<li>Added Line Height Option to Button Group</li>\n<li>Added Option to Collapse Buttons</li>\n<li>Fixed Icon Issue in Button Group</li>\n<li>Increased Maximum Font Size Limit</li>\n<li>Fixed Font Weight Value Error</li>\n<li>Fixed Fatal Error Caused by Gutenberg Plugin</li>\n<li>Fixed Unescaped Character Preview in Post Grid</li>\n<li>Improved Handling of Unique Block IDs</li>\n<li>Added Left/Right Margin Options to Section Column</li>\n<li>Added Controls for Responsive Alignment to Advanced Heading Block</li>\n<li>Fixed Vertical Alignment in Section Block</li>\n<li>Fixed Alignment Issue in Social Sharing Block</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0 &#8211; 2019-01-18</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added Section Block, with Template Library</li>\n<li>Added Advanced Heading Block</li>\n<li>Added Button Group Block</li>\n<li>Deprecated Notice, Click to Tweet, Chart, Accordion, blocks</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4 &#8211; 2018-12-07</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed dependencies issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3 &#8211; 2018-12-07</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixes issue with Posts Grid block displaying wrong author</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2 &#8211; 2018-12-05</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed Notice Block and Font Awesome Icons</li>\n<li>Optimized build size</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1 &#8211; 2018-10-29</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Bug fixed with Google Map block.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; 2018-10-17</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds docker env.</li>\n<li>Adds hash back.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:11:\"screenshots\";s:845:\"<ol><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2019293\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2019293\" alt=\"Otter Blocks\"></a><p>Otter Blocks</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2019293\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2019293\" alt=\"Section Block\"></a><p>Section Block</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2046920\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2046920\" alt=\"Template Library\"></a><p>Template Library</p></li><li><a href=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2019293\"><img src=\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2019293\" alt=\"Pre-built Section\"></a><p>Pre-built Section</p></li></ol>\";s:7:\"reviews\";s:13413:\"<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Google Map</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mengyong888\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aad323cb475e7e83b419edf3b3941ec8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aad323cb475e7e83b419edf3b3941ec8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mengyong888\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mengyong888</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">July 2, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Google map is not showing on Internet Explorer</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Working as expeced - Thanks!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joebitcoinorg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/810bc0e9b727111e0737f287589bff12?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/810bc0e9b727111e0737f287589bff12?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joebitcoinorg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">joebitcoinorg</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">June 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'m working on a project called Remedycoin.com  and i think we can create money to reward open source software projects..</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and great support, easy to use theme</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dhikademocrat\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/947c5d43de40158e3a7fe8f9a76feac1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/947c5d43de40158e3a7fe8f9a76feac1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dhikademocrat\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dhikademocrat</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">June 11, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The developer @HardeepAsrani is a superb helper - aside from being the developer of course. I\'m not a coder and can use the theme to help my mom build a website for her salon. A little hiccup here and there but he\'s always responsive and ready to help solve your problem.\n\nDefinitely recommended!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dido4012\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87dbcc1e572056a1ce226c59775dc54a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/87dbcc1e572056a1ce226c59775dc54a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dido4012\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Dian Tankov <small>(dido4012)</small></a> em <span class=\"review-date\">June 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">It\'s easy to use and works perfectly.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Well optimized for Speed!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phillt\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/208fde0a82e04e5a75869192f2e56bdc?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/208fde0a82e04e5a75869192f2e56bdc?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/phillt\" class=\"reviewer-name\">phillt</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">June 9, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Finally a good Gutenberg Block Plugin! Simple, Fast &amp; Efficient!\n\nWhat i really appreciate is the only one small CSS file of 29,7kb! Loads very fast so it\'s really well optimized for speed!!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Навязливо</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/loowqp\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea95e8ed21e8f1a1257c68a7622d9d2e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ea95e8ed21e8f1a1257c68a7622d9d2e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/loowqp\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Roman Lemberg <small>(loowqp)</small></a> em <span class=\"review-date\">May 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">За навязливість</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome premium blocks for free</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kuro\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/637cda9296b9a782c8b0d753be31ee60?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/637cda9296b9a782c8b0d753be31ee60?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kuro\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kuro</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">May 12, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I love it this block collection.\n\nGreat work!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works as expected</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/geost\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09bc3f7cd9771069a7975f9c5638327c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/09bc3f7cd9771069a7975f9c5638327c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/geost\" class=\"reviewer-name\">AtrumGeost <small>(Geost)</small></a> em <span class=\"review-date\">April 23, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Using it with the Neve theme. Nice integration with Gutenberg.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thanks</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/duveit\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e406193a2aa7cc79d5e65a923c8bc2c5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e406193a2aa7cc79d5e65a923c8bc2c5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/duveit\" class=\"reviewer-name\">duveit</a> em <span class=\"review-date\">March 31, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Everything works well, thank you ;o)</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It just works</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 de 5 estrelas\" data-title-template=\"%s de 5 estrelas\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sourav926\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/004c65c5ebd36933bdb7a64ca742aa6d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/004c65c5ebd36933bdb7a64ca742aa6d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sourav926\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Keramot UL Islam <small>(sourav926)</small></a> em <span class=\"review-date\">February 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin shows what we can do with Gutenberg. Eagerly looking forward to more Blocks and Templates.\n	<ul><li>In future, It can be a better competitor of page builders.</li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:114:\"Create beautiful and attracting posts, pages, and landing pages with Gutenberg Blocks and Template Library&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2019293\";s:7:\"caption\";s:12:\"Otter Blocks\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2019293\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Section Block\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2046920\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Template Library\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-4.png?rev=2019293\";s:7:\"caption\";s:17:\"Pre-built Section\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:15:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.5\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.5.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.2.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.2.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.2.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.2.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.2.3.zip\";}s:7:\"banners\";a:2:{s:3:\"low\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/banner-772x250.png?rev=2019296\";s:4:\"high\";s:68:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/banner-1544x500.png?rev=2019294\";}s:5:\"icons\";a:2:{s:2:\"1x\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=2019293\";s:2:\"2x\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/icon-256x256.png?rev=2019293\";}}', 'no'),
